epi_cancel_right
----------------

l1: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ epi (g ∘ f) $ by ax
l2: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ ∀ x ((alpha ∘ (g ∘ f) ~ x ∘ (g ∘ f)) → (alpha ~ x)) $ by all_elim(x := $ y $) [l1]
l3: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ (alpha ∘ (g ∘ f) ~ beta ∘ (g ∘ f)) → (alpha ~ beta) $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g $ by ax
l5: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ (alpha ∘ g) ∘ f ~ (beta ∘ g) ∘ f $ by comp_right [l4]
l6: $ epi (g ∘ f) , (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) ⊢ alpha ~ beta $ by imp_elim [l3, l5]
l7: $ epi (g ∘ f) ⊢ (alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) → (alpha ~ beta) $ by imp_intro [l6]
l8: $ epi (g ∘ f) ⊢ ∀ beta ((alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) → (alpha ~ beta)) $ by all_intro [l7]
l9: $ epi (g ∘ f) ⊢ ∀ alpha ∀ beta ((alpha ∘ g ~ beta ∘ g) → (alpha ~ beta)) $ by all_intro [l8]
